-- Obama: 2012 budget a downpayment for fiscal reform
-- 
-- Mon Feb 14, 2011 10:38am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/02/14/us-usa-budget-obama-downpayment-idUSTRE71D3YB20110214

 

 PARKVILLE, Maryland  (Reuters) - U.S. President Barack Obama said on Monday his fiscal 2012 budget was a "downpayment" on what was needed to get the United States on a strong fiscal path, saying Democrats and Republicans must work together to do more. 

 (Reporting by  Patricia Zengerle , writing by Jeff Mason, Editing by Sandra Maler)